619
00:26:32,740 --> 00:26:34,740
doesn't have any sources

620
00:26:34,740 --> 00:26:37,740
in the same sense that the electric field does.

621
00:26:37,740 --> 00:26:40,740
It doesn't emanate out from a point,

622
00:26:40,740 --> 00:26:43,740
it tends to wind around things.

623
00:26:43,740 --> 00:26:46,740
Okay, the next equation

