00:26:46,740 --> 00:26:48,740
is an equation similar to this,

625
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:51,740
but it involves del cross of the magnetic field,

626
00:26:51,740 --> 00:26:54,740
and it's equal to plus

627
00:26:54,740 --> 00:26:57,740
dE by dt.

628
00:26:57,740 --> 00:27:00,740
So these two equations look very similar.

629
00:27:00,740 --> 00:27:02,740
It's almost as though you interchanged

