00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:08,740
There's a sign difference between them.

633
00:27:08,740 --> 00:27:11,740
If you just interchanged the magnetic and electric field,

634
00:27:11,740 --> 00:27:14,740
you'd get the wrong sign here.

635
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:17,740
And the last one is just

636
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:19,740
del dot E equals zero.

637
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:24,740
And this is the same equation

638
00:27:24,740 --> 00:27:27,740
in quite parallel with the magnetic field here.

639
00:27:27,740 --> 00:27:29,740
These are the basic Maxwell's equations,

640
00:27:29,740 --> 00:27:31,740
but these are the Maxwell's equations

641
00:27:31,740 --> 00:27:33,740
when there are no charges around,

642
00:27:33,740 --> 00:27:36,740
in the absence of charges and currents.

643
00:27:36,740 --> 00:27:38,740
Let me put back in

644
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:40,740
what happens when there are charges and currents.

645
00:27:40,740 --> 00:27:41,740
In other words,

646
00:27:41,740 --> 00:27:43,740
these are the equations that are called

647
00:27:43,740 --> 00:27:46,740
