648
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:49,740
They describe electric and magnetic fields

649
00:27:49,740 --> 00:27:51,740
in completely infinite terms.

650
00:27:51,740 --> 00:27:53,740
They have no electric charges,

651
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:55,740
no currents.

652
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:57,740
Let me just tell you now

653
00:27:57,740 --> 00:27:59,740
what happens if you add in

654
00:27:59,740 --> 00:28:01,740
