655
00:28:01,740 --> 00:28:03,740
some electric currents,

656
00:28:03,740 --> 00:28:05,740
and so forth.

657
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:07,740
They do have an effect on things.

658
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:09,740
And so, for example,

