00:28:11,740 --> 00:28:13,740
the actual thing that goes.

661
00:28:13,740 --> 00:28:15,740
The charge density

662
00:28:15,740 --> 00:28:17,740
is called rho,

663
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:19,740
and it's the amount of

664
00:28:19,740 --> 00:28:21,740
electric charge per unit volume.

665
00:28:21,740 --> 00:28:23,740
At every point in space,

666
00:28:23,740 --> 00:28:25,740
there may or may not be some charge.

667
00:28:25,740 --> 00:28:27,740
In every little cell of space,

668
00:28:27,740 --> 00:28:29,740
