00:29:41,740 --> 00:29:43,740
in every reference frame,

705
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:45,740
and in every reference frame

706
00:29:45,740 --> 00:29:47,740
they say the speed of light is exactly the same.

707
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:49,740
So let's see if we can recast

708
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:51,740
these four equations

709
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:53,740
which is the same in every reference frame.

710
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:55,740
We have the tools to do it.

711
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:57,740
What we have to remember

712
00:29:57,740 --> 00:29:59,740
is that

713
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:01,740
the electric and magnetic fields

714
00:30:01,740 --> 00:30:03,740
combine together, we did this last time,

