00:30:07,740 --> 00:30:09,740
into an anti-symmetric tensor.

718
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:11,740
So let's remind ourselves of that.

719
00:30:13,740 --> 00:30:15,740
Anti-symmetric tensor,

